                    "text": "A judge node \u2014 ideally a stronger model like Opus \u2014 synthesizes the final answer from the complete transcript, integrating the strongest points from both sides."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Add a lightweight consensus check after each round to terminate early if agents converge, avoiding unnecessary LLM calls."
                  }
